Janab-e-Alaa, Tunday Kebabs are a culinary masterpiece from the heart of Lucknow. They're named after a one-armed chef who created them for a Nawab who had lost his teeth. These kebabs are so soft and tender that they melt in your mouth, making them a true delight for food lovers.

The original Tunday Kababi shop in the old Chowk area is a must-visit for kebab enthusiasts. It's where you can experience the authentic taste of this legendary dish. So, if you're ever in Lucknow, be sure to give Tunday Kebabs a try. You won't be disappointed!"}

